l; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Open BlueDragon + Railo + ColdFusion on Tomcat</a><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">Sean Corfield&#39;s blog:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://corfield.org/blog/index.cfm/do/blog.entry/entry/Railo__ColdFusion_on_JRun\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(255, 135, 6); text-decoration: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26.399999618530273px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">Railo + OpenBD + ColdFusion on JRun</a><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0.5em 0px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(60, 62, 64); font-size: 2.4em; text-transform: uppercase; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.01em; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">OTHER SETUPS</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><b style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26.399999618530273px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">EAR deployment</b><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">&nbsp;ColdShen:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://coldshen.com/blog/index.cfm/2008/8/2/Deploying-Railo-as-an-EAR-under-JBoss-5\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(255, 135, 6); text-decoration: none; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26.399999618530273px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\" target=\"_blank\">Deploying Railo as an EAR under JBoss 5</a></p>\r\n',0,'2014-08-11 10:33:02','2014-08-11 10:33:02',NULL,1,NULL,'MICROSOFT WINDOWS\n\n32bit\nRailo blog: Configuring IIS6 with Railo\nRailo blog: Railo and Apache\nDoug Boude: Railo with Tomcat 6 and Windows 2K8 with IIS7 ...'),(14,'Tip of the week: loops','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">With Railo 4.0 we introduced a change that allows you always loop over index and item. I am sure many of you don&#39;t know from the top of your head what to use when using cfloop array / collection wether it is index or item what you are using as a loop variable and what that variable contains.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">To clear things up, when using cfloop array, you have to use index for your variable and it will contain the item. And when you use cfloop collection, you have to use item and it will contain, well, the index (the keys of the struct). So exactly the opposite of what their names suggest.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">So Railo now allows you to always (except for queries) use index AND item. And the index then will contain the index and the item, well, the item. This in all reality means that for arrays and collections they will contain the opposite of what they contained before. Let&#39;s have a look at the following examples (and as of the latest Railo 4.2 beta, it can be written in the latest proposed tag notaion in cfscript):&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<code style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px 0px; color: rgb(0, 153, 0); font-size: 0.85em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 16.575000762939453px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span class=\"cc_cftag\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: maroon; background: transparent;\">&lt;cfscript&gt;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />\r\ncfloop(array=<span class=\"cc_value\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: blue; background: transparent;\">&quot;#[&#39;a&#39;,&#39;b&#39;,&#39;c&#39;,&#39;d&#39;]#&quot;</span>, index=<span class=\"cc_value\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: blue; background: transparent;\">&quot;local.i&quot;</span>, item=<span class=\"cc_value\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: blue; background: transparent;\">&quot;local.sElement&quot;</span>) {<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;writeOutput(i &amp;&nbsp;<span class=\"cc_value\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: blue; background: transparent;\">&quot;: &quot;</span>&nbsp;&amp; sElement &amp;&nbsp;<span class=\"cc_value\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: blue; background: transparent;\">&quot;<span class=\"cc_normaltag\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: navy; background: transparent;\">&lt;br&gt;</span>&quot;</span>);<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />\r\n}<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\" />\r\n<span class=\"cc_cftag\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: maroon; background: transparent;\">&lt;/cfscript&gt;</span></code><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">&nbsp;</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<b style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 26.399999618530273px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">This will output:</b><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">1: a</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">2: b</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">3: c</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">4: d</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\">and the following notations are allowed as well:</span><br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<br style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(120, 122, 125); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26.399999618530273px;\" />\r\n<code style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 10px 0px; color: rgb(0, 153, 0); font-size: 0.85em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 16.575000762939453px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; b